title: Meant to Be
overview: What will happen if four equally handsome guys fall for one girl? How can that girl choose just one?Billie is a typical millennial with issues in life. Her parents Wilton and Amelia are not in good terms. Her brother Bats is jobless. So, she works hard to make ends meet for her family.Despite setbacks, Billie is thankful to her cousin Mariko who has been her confidant and pillar of strength. But their friendship will be put to the test when Billie meets four guys of different nationalities who will compete against each other to win her heart.
